title: backgroundDNS tunnels
extract: /ˈtʌnəl ˈटनल्/ Word forms: tunnels, tunnelling, tunnelled or [Am] tunneling, tunneled. countable noun. A tunnel is a long passage which has been made under the ground, usually through a hill or under the sea.
